{{short description|4th-century BC Roman consul}}
{{unreferenced|date=June 2013}}

'''Lucius Aemilius L.f. Mamercinus''' was a [[Roman Republic|Roman]] [[Roman patrician|patrician]] who served as [[Roman Consul|consul]] in 366 and 363 BC.

